|-
||[[中國|中國]]{{flagicon|China}}
|-
||[[德國|德國]]{{flagicon|Germany}}
|-
||[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]{{flagicon|Netherlands }}
|-
||[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]{{flagicon|New Zealand}}
|}

